Zsh 安装1 下载 msys 版 zsh 解压，获得 usr etc 将 usr etc 分别放入 git bash 根目录下，与原有同名文件夹合并 Zsh-autosuggestions2 利用 Git 下载插件 git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions ~/.zsh/zsh-autosuggestions 在 .zshrc 中添加下面一行 source ~/.zsh/zsh-autosuggestions/zsh-autosuggestions.zsh Zsh-syntax-highlighting3 利用 Git 下载插件 git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git ~/.zsh/zsh-syntax-highlighting 在 .zshrc 中添加下面一行 source ./zsh-syntax-highlighting/zsh-syntax-highlighting.zsh https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/455925403&#160;&#x21a9;&#xfe0e;
https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions/blob/master/INSTALL.md#manual-git-clone&#160;&#x21a9;&#xfe0e;
https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting/blob/master/INSTALL.md&#160;&#x21a9;&#xfe0e;
